Title: Darin Gaub to Newsmax: Putin Cannot Be Trusted as Russia Ukraine Talks Advance
Description: Speaking on Newsmax's Wake Up America Early, Gaub said the diplomatic push led by U.S. Special Envoy Steve Witkoff will face significant obstacles because Putin is unlikely to reveal his true intentions until the moment a deal is finalized.
URL: https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/darin-gaub-putin-russia/2025/11/28/id/1236341/

Title: Trump 'is set to recognise Russian control over Crimea and other occupied Ukrainian territories in bid to secure deal with Putin to end war'
Description: Officials close to the talks say the US president has dispatched his peace envoy, Steve Witkoff, along with his son-in-law, Jared Kushner , to set out the proposal to Putin in Moscow.
URL: https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-15335043/Trump-set-recognise-Russian-control-Crimea-occupied-Ukrainian-territories-bid-secure-deal-Putin-end-war.html

Title: Steve McBee Sr. Spends Last Thanksgiving on His Ranch Before Prison
Description: Steve McBee Sr. spent his last Thanksgiving at his ranch before he has to report to prison on Dec. 1. In October, the 'McBee Dynasty' star was sentenced to two years in prison in his crop insurance fraud case.
URL: https://people.com/steve-mcbee-sr-spends-last-thanksgiving-ranch-before-prison-11856960

Title: Fleitz to Newsmax: Zelenskyy Ready to Sign Peace Deal Amid Breakthrough in Talks
Description: Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy is ready to sign the emerging U.S.-backed peace plan — a step former Trump NSC chief of staff Fred Fleitz says marks “real progress” driven by President Donald Trump and special envoy Steve Witkoff.
URL: https://www.newsmax.com/newsmax-tv/fred-fleitz-volodymyr-zelenskyy-ukraine/2025/11/28/id/1236335/

Title: McBee Dynasty's Steve McBee Sr. Got Prison Advice From Todd Chrisley
Description: As 'McBee Dynasty' star Steve McBee Sr. prepares for his two-year prison sentence, he is getting advice from fellow reality star Todd Chrisley
URL: https://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/mcbee-dynastys-steve-mcbee-sr-got-prison-advice-from-todd-chrisley/
